data.description: NEW PRICE & CARPET ALLOWANCE!!! Come see this elegant Pineville home in Legacy Pointe Subdivision, where pride of ownership is easily seen. This three-bedroom, two-bath home, with a sunroom and office, features 2,260 heated square feet with a double-car garage and stainless steel Maytag appliances. The soaring ceilings will grab anyone's attention, and the sunroom is just waiting for you to sit down with your coffee or iced tea. The kitchen is open to the living area, and French doors open up and lead to a covered backyard patio for family time and gatherings. The master bedroom suite is a must-see with its own gas fireplace, separate attached office/nursery, and a large master bath. The neighborhood is classy and quiet, and the traffic is extremely light. This is not one you will want to pass up seeing. Zoned for JI Barron, Pineville Junior High, and Pineville High School. Sellers are willing to grant a $4000.00 thousand dollar carpet allowance to buyers. Split Floor Plan, 3 bed 2 bath with bonus rooms. Thanks for looking and please call to schedule your own showing today.
